    <div class="well" id="wintabber_tab_y" >

        
        <a name="002826"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.wintabber.com/">WinTabber - Tab your terminal, shell, browser or favorite application</a></h4>

        

        <p>Can be used with PuTTY to create a tabbed interface.  Since I usually have four or five ssh shells open at a time, this&#8217;ll help me keep track of things.</p>

