    <div class="well" id="clamwin_free_an" >

        
        <a name="002592"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.clamwin.com/">ClamWin Free Antiviru</a></h4>

        

        <p>Free and Free antivirus for WIndows, based on ClamAV.  Imagine Norton Antivirus, but without all the masses of shite that slows down your PC.  Doesn&#8217;t include &#8220;on-access&#8221; file scanning, but I&#8217;m happy with that.</p>

