<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jun/13/">&#x27a0;</a> June 13, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="gparted_livecd" >

        
        <a name="002582"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://gparted.sourceforge.net/livecd.php">GParted -- LiveCD</a></h4>

        

        <p>Manoman is this handy.  Boot up off the live CD and repartition your hard drive on the fly without losing data.  It&#8217;s like PartitionMagic, but free, free and it doesn&#8217;t corrupt your data!</p>

